page.title: 19Young Peoples' Groups,Yeovil
page.content: {Swimming Club.}Yeovil Swimming Club meet on Monday nights at 6.00pm.There are 4 width groups (beginners,turtles, tadpoles and dolphins).They take up 3 quarters of the pool.At the deep end a diving group practices.At 8.20 the lengths groups start,they have 25 minutes,& then the Yeovil Squad has a turn.They are the swimmers who represent Yeovil in galas.I am in the Yeovil squad. Jean Clancy. { {Disco Dancing.}I go disco dancing from 7.00_8.00pm on Wednesdays.When we have warmed up we do dances like Arm Pushes,Kick Across,Roly Poly,Finger Snaps,Thriller,Open the Door & Maniac. You can take Bronze,Silver & Gold awards in Disco Dancing. Sharon Bowring.
